Our Vision

To establish a sustainable business environment in KNU-controlled areas that promotes social, economic, and environmental development for both entrepreneurs and local communities.

2

Our Mission

To provide a transparent and fair business registration system that ensures the authenticity and reliability of business records while promoting compliance with KNU regulations and policies.

3

Our Objectives

The objectives of the KECS are 1) Establish accessible business registration system for all businesses in KNU-controlled area. 2) Promote transparency and accountability in business activities. More ...
